display the database ordered by price. 
SELECT price FROM clothing 
ORDER BY price desc;

what is the sum of articles of clothing in the database? 
SELECT SUM (quantity) FROM clothing 

what is the average cost for an article of clothing in the database? 
SELECT AVG(price) FROM clothing 
